casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, State Agriculture Development Committee, County of Hunterdon and Township of Franklin, Plaintiffs,
v.
QUAKER VALLEY FARMS, LLC and David den Hollander, Defendants-Movants. M-369/370 September Term 2018
078517 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 6, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-369) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's opinion (M-370) is denied.
